<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="character-hero heaven-glow">
  <div class="container character-shell">
    <div class="character-top">
      <div class="character-portrait-wrap">
        <div class="character-portrait">
          <img src="/images/cover.png" alt="Josiah" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="character-meta">
        <div class="faction-row">
          <span class="badge badge-heaven">Heaven</span>
          <span class="badge">Chosen Vessel</span>
        </div>

        <h1>Josiah</h1>
        <p class="character-subtitle">The Child of Prophecy</p>
        <div class="power-rank">Power Tier: Destiny-Bound</div>

        <p class="character-intro">
          Josiah is the living collision point between prophecy, bloodline, and supernatural war.
          After the sky breaks open, his life becomes the trigger point for powers that have waited
          across ages to rise.
        </p>

        <div class="character-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Return Home</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/about">About the Author</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="character-panel-section">
  <div class="container panel-grid">
    <div class="elite-panel">
      <h2>Lore</h2>
      <p class="lore-text">
        Josiah is not merely important to the prophecy — he is one of its living keys. His survival
        is not random. His awakening is tied to an ancient war stretching across Heaven, Earth, and
        the unseen realm.
      </p>

      <div class="power-grid">
        <div class="power-card power-heaven">
          <h3>Destiny Link</h3>
          <p>Bound to a prophecy that reshapes the fate of multiple realms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="power-card power-heaven">
          <h3>Awakening</h3>
          <p>His true identity unfolds as the war intensifies around him.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="power-card power-heaven">
          <h3>Bloodline</h3>
          <p>A heritage connected to powers older than nations and empires.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="power-card power-heaven">
          <h3>Survival Instinct</h3>
          <p>Even under pressure, he remains central to the battle’s future.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="quote-box">
        “He is not just in the prophecy. He is one of the reasons it moves.”
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="elite-panel">
      <h2>Profile</h2>

      <div class="stats-list">
        <div class="stat-row">
          <span class="stat-label">Faction</span>
          <span class="stat-value">Heaven</span>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-row">
          <span class="stat-label">Role</span>
          <span class="stat-value">The Child of Prophecy</span>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-row">
          <span class="stat-label">Primary Theme</span>
          <span class="stat-value">Destiny / Awakening / War</span>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-row">
          <span class="stat-label">Threat Level</span>
          <span class="stat-value">World-Shifting</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>